body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:
John M. Carlson to C. H. Ulbrath: Southport and Pratt Avenues. Price, $5,000.
H. H. Hallman to John H. Assmunsen: Waveland and Hoyne Avenues. Price, $2,950.
John P. Larsen to Christ Nelson: Fullerton and Spaulding Avenues. Price, $1,750.
A. O. Anderson to Niels Nielsen: Erie and 32nd Avenues. Price, $700.
Minnie Hansen to W. Brictche: Bishop and 60th Streets. Price, $5,000.
Hans A. Hansen to Milton French: Peoria and 62nd Streets. Price, $3,250.
Magnus A. Unseth to C. F. L. Stephan: Maplewood Avenue and Cherry Place. Price, $3,950.
